reviewText: I have many DVDs of about dinosaurs, most of them quite good. I did not even keep this one, the animation was too poor. That should tell you all you want to know about this DVD.
Seen one, seen them all. A costly reworking of the original. The monsters are as expected, the goriness as expected.

When I purchased the "Dinosaurs Of The Jurassic Collection", I really wasn't sure what to expect. However, I soon found myself learning all sorts of information that I didn't already know about the different dinosaurs of the Jurassic period. I was also impressed with the computer graphics and how realistic everything looked.
